summary:
Workrelated: Museumprofessional, collecting and deaccessioning (ontzamelen/afstoten), collectionmanagement, collection policy plans, lectures, workshops and publications, (complex) restauration and conservation projects, silver expert, material culture.
Other interests: travelling and expeditions (+ writing about it), 3Dprinting, diving and photography.
